Source: pg-accumulator
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/Treedo/pg_accumulator

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-accumulator
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-accumulator
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Accumulation registers for PostgreSQL
  pg_accumulator is a data accounting engine for PostgreSQL. It provides
  declarative accumulation registers for balance and turnover tracking across
  arbitrary dimensions, with transactional consistency and optimized reads.
